INSERT INTO met_column VALUES('96','Company profile','about','','95','0','1','0','0','0','0','0','','','<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>About us</strong></h1><p><br/></p><p>Mito enterprise station building system (formerly known as Metinfo enterprise website management system) has become the mainstream tool for many enterprises since it was released in 2009.</p><p><strong>The mobile phone system tiktok supports 1 web sites to be easily synchronized to 10 terminal displays (computer, mobile phone, tablet, micro official website, WeChat applet, Baidu applet, Alipay applet, byte beating small program [today\'s headlines, jitter], 360 small programs, QQ applet), open source free, suitable for building professional websites.</strong></p><p>Mito enterprise station building system adopts PHP + MySQL architecture, supports SQLite database, the whole station has built-in seo search engine optimization mechanism, supports user-defined language (all kinds of languages in the world), supports visual editing management, and has common functional modules (Introduction module, article module, product module, download module, picture module, recruitment module, online message Feedback system, online communication, friendship link, website map, member and authority management, tag), powerful SEO and pseudo static setting functions, support custom website color style, support custom banner chart and data call by column, support bottom menu of mobile phone, support independent secondary development of users, and support online upgrade of business template. The system has built-in standard application plug-in development interface, rich free plug-ins and charging plug-ins, such as SMS interface, robots file modification, template making assistant, applet, payment interface, mall module, system clinic, image acceleration, website advertising plug-ins, etc. Whether you\'re a technology tycoon or a website builder, you can use Metinfo to quickly build a professional website with complete functions.</p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"../upload/202002/1582957948990204.jpg\" data-width=\"1180\" width=\"1180\" data-height=\"664\" height=\"664\" alt=\"1516066438664023.jpg\" title=\"1582957948990204.jpg\"/></p><p>We adhere to the core values of \"creating value for partners\", and take \"honesty, tolerance, innovation and service\" as the enterprise spirit, and create value for e-commerce and information service industry through independent innovation and sincere cooperation.</p><p><br/></p><p><strong>About \"creating value for partners\"</strong></p><p>We believe that customers, suppliers, company shareholders, company employees and other units and individuals who have cooperative relations with themselves are their own partners, and only through efforts to create value for partners, can they reflect their own value and achieve development and success.</p><p><br/></p><p><strong>On \"honesty, tolerance, innovation and service\"</strong></p><p>We believe that honesty is the basis of all cooperation, tolerance is the premise to solve problems, innovation is the weapon to develop business, and service is the basis to create value.</p>','Company profile / about us mitro enterprise station building system (formerly known as Metinfo mitro enterprise station building system) has become the mainstream tool for many enterprises since it was released in 2009. The mobile phone system tiktok supports 1 web sites to be easily synchronized to 10 terminal displays (computer, mobile phone, tablet, micro official website, WeChat applet, Baidu applet, Alipay applet, byte beating small program [today\'s headlines, jitter], 360 small programs, QQ applet), open source free, suitable for building professional websites. Mito enterprise station building system adopts PHP + MySQL architecture,','','','1','0','2','','0','0','','','1','en','','0','0','','0','14','','','','0','0','');
