INSERT INTO met_column VALUES('328','Company profile','about','','327','0','1','0','0','0','0','0','','','<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>/about us</strong></h1><p><br/></p><p>Since its release in 2009, mitow enterprise website building system (formerly known as MetInfo enterprise website management system) has become the mainstream tool for many enterprises to build websites.</p><p><strong>M extension enterprise website system support 1 content easily synchronized to 10 kinds of terminal display (computer, mobile phone, tablet, micro website, WeChat applet, baidu small programs, pay treasure to small procedures, bytes to beat small [today\'s headlines, trill], 360 small programs, QQ small program), free, open source suitable for use in building professional websites.</strong></p><p>M extension enterprise website system USES PHP + MySQL architecture, support the SQLite database, total station with built-in SEO search engine optimization mechanism, support user-defined language (global languages), support for visual editing management, has a corporate web site commonly used function module (profile module, the article module, product module, download module, image module, recruiting module, online message, feedback systems, online communication, links, site map, members and permissions management, the TAG label), powerful SEO and pseudo static Settings, support custom website color style, Support customized Banner chart and data call according to the column, support the bottom menu of the phone, support users\' independent secondary development, support online upgrade of business templates. The system has a built-in standard application plug-in development interface, with a wealth of free plug-ins and paid plug-ins, such as SMS interface, robots file modification, template making assistant, small program, payment interface, mall module, system clinic, image acceleration, website advertising plug-in, etc. Whether you\'re a tech geek or a web developer, you can use MetInfo to quickly build a fully functional, responsive professional website.</p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"../upload/202002/1582957948990204.jpg\" data-width=\"1180\" width=\"1180\" data-height=\"664\" height=\"664\" alt=\"1516066438664023.jpg\" title=\"1582957948990204.jpg\"/></p><p>We uphold the core values of \"creating value for partners\", and take \"honesty, tolerance, innovation, service\" as the spirit of enterprise, through independent innovation and sincere cooperation to create value for e-commerce and information service industry.</p><p><br/></p><p><strong>About \"creating value for partners\"</strong></p><p>We believe that customers, suppliers, company shareholders, company employees and all the units and individuals who have cooperation with us are our own partners. Only by creating value for our partners can we reflect our own value and achieve development and success.</p><p><br/></p><p><strong>On \"honesty, tolerance, innovation and service\"</strong></p><p>We believe that good faith is the basis of all cooperation, tolerance is the premise of solving problems, innovation is the weapon of development, and service is the root of creating value.</p>','Since its release in 2009, MetInfo | meter enterprise station building system has become the mainstream tool for many enterprises to build stations. M extension enterprise website system support 1 content easily synchronized to 10 kinds of terminal display (computer, mobile phone, tablet, micro website, WeChat applet, baidu small programs, pay treasure to small procedures, bytes to beat small [today\'s headlines, trill], 360 small programs, QQ small program), free, open source suitable for use in building professional websites. Mituo enterprise station construction system adopts PHP + MySQL architecture.','','','1','0','2','','0','0','','','1','id','','0','0','','0','14','','','','0','0','');
