INSERT INTO met_news VALUES('44','The combination and application of intelligent vehicle and intelligent transportation','','','From the perspective of automobile, let\'s talk about my views on intelligent automobile and intelligent transportation. You know that automobile has a history of more than 100 years, but automobile is actually developed through continuous revolution and innovation. You can see from ppt that the first automobile was born in 1886, where is the era of automobile innovation, now you know Maybach, Citroen, etc It\'s all the inventor\'s name. It\'s the European who invented the car. But in the first and second years of the last century, the famous Henry Ford of the United States improved the way of automobile production. In fact, he did not improve the way of automobile production. He created automobile users','<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"../upload/202002/1582286273462743.jpg\" data-width=\"900\" data-height=\"383\" title=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">From the perspective of automobile, let&#39;s talk about my views on intelligent automobile and intelligent transportation. You know that automobile has a history of more than 100 years, but automobile is actually developed through continuous revolution and innovation. You can see from ppt that the first automobile was born in 1886, where is the era of automobile innovation, now you know Maybach, Citroen, etc It&#39;s all the inventor&#39;s name. It&#39;s the European who invented the car. But in the past few years, the famous Henry Ford of the United States improved the way of automobile production. In fact, he did not improve the way of automobile production. He created the users of automobile, which made the automobile expand rapidly in the United States according to the way of assembly line of mass production. In the 1970s and 1980s, Toyota&#39;s elite production mode brought revolution to the automobile. Ford and Toyota&#39;s influence on the automobile industry not only affects the automobile industry, but also affects the whole manufacturing industry. Now it should be said that the coming of another revolutionary period is the technology of mobile interconnection and new energy technology. Here I would like to emphasize that the technology of new energy vehicles or electric vehicles has been given enough attention all over the world, because Obama attaches great importance and leaders of all countries attach great importance to it, but the mobile Internet technology and intelligent vehicle technology have not been given enough attention, so I would like to participate in such a meeting and share my views.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">This ppt refers to another classification method, which divides the industry into two categories, one is based on physics, the other is based on technology, and the car just stands in the middle, indicating that it has the characteristics of both technology and physical integration. This is a sign of the development of the car itself. For example, before the mobile Internet, the car was an electromechanical integration product, and the car was not a simple mechanical product for a long time. In the 1960s, when the club of Rome wrote the growth limit, it defined the automobile as the sunset industry. In fact, the automobile is a sunrise industry. Now there are two major changes in the use of automobiles, one is the integration of mobile Internet technology from its design and manufacturing services, the other is the transformation of automobiles from a simple means of transportation to a solution through mobile Internet technology and intelligent Internet connected automobiles, so as to meet the three important purposes of social security, energy conservation and wind resistance.</span></p><p><br/></p>','106','107','0','0','0','0','../upload/202002/1582286273462743.jpg','','0','admin',